            <div data-ui-tablist class="ui-accordion" data-ui-transition="collapse">
                <!-- faq-1 -->
                <div class="ui-accordion-item">
                    <button data-ui-tablist-tab class="ui-accordion-header">What types of events do you cover?
                    </button>
                    <div data-ui-tablist-tabpanel>
                        <div class="ui-accordion-body"> We capture a wide range of events, including corporate conferences, product launches, award ceremonies, trade shows, and private gatherings. Whatever your event, we ensure all the key moments are captured. </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- faq-2 -->
                <div class="ui-accordion-item">
                    <button data-ui-tablist-tab class="ui-accordion-header">How far in advance should we book?</button>
                    <div data-ui-tablist-tabpanel hidden>
                        <div class="ui-accordion-body">To secure your preferred date, we recommend booking at least 2-4 weeks in advance. However, we understand that last-minute events can pop up, so we’ll do our best to accommodate your needs.</div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <!-- faq-3 -->
                <div class="ui-accordion-item">
                    <button data-ui-tablist-tab class="ui-accordion-header">Can you provide same-day photo delivery?</button>
                    <div data-ui-tablist-tabpanel hidden>
                        <div class="ui-accordion-body">Yes! We offer a selection of photos delivered by the end of the same business day or the following day for immediate use on social media or for press releases.</div>
